<h2>Empty Colgroups</h2>
<p>Add "empty" col elements that represents the columns before the columns you want to style:</p>

<table style="width: 100%;">
<colgroup>
  <col span="3">
  <col span="2" style="background-color: pink">
</colgroup>
<tr>
<th>MON</th>
<th>TUE</th>
<th>WED</th>
<th>THU</th>
<th>FRI</th>
<th>SAT</th>
<th>SUN</th>
</tr>
