CODE-39
--------------------

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>

<h2>The start attribute</h2>
<p>By default, an ordered list will start counting from 1. Use the start attribute to start counting from a specified number:</p>

<ol start="50">
  <li>Coffee</li>
  <li>Tea</li>
  <li>Milk</li>
</ol>

<ol type="I" start="50">
  <li>Coffee</li>
  <li>Tea</li>
  <li>Milk</li>
</ol>

</body>
</html>

CODE-40
--------------------

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>

<h2>A Nested List</h2>
<p>Lists can be nested (list inside list):</p>

<ol>
  <li>Coffee</li>
  <li>Tea
    <ol>
      <li>Black tea</li>
      <li>Green tea</li>
    </ol>
  </li>
  <li>Milk</li>
</ol>

</body>
</html>

CODE-41
--------------------

